WorkItem.Description:
Converting a word 2011 document with a list to html renders the list items as paragraphs

e.g.

1)	Buy pants
	a.	Must be blue
	b.	Must be flared
2)	Buy shirt
	a.	Must be white
3)	Buy tie
	a.	Must be awful
	b.	Offensive
	c.	Stripy

Becomes:

Buy pants

Must be blue

Must be flared

Buy shirt

Must be white

Buy tie

Must be awful

Offensive

Stripy
WorkItem.Summary: Converting word to html does not render lists as lists
